{"tid":417769,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple iPhone 8 Plus 驚現電池漲起致螢幕爆裂事故","createTime":"2017-09-29T03:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T12:23:06.000Z","uid":137694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccaa8a9183c158b6528b9c307077f4448a340135","tid":417769,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"Apple iPhone 8 系列驚現電池漲起致螢幕爆裂事故！日本網友 まごころ 在其 Twitter 上表示，當其打開新手機 iPhone 8 Plus 後，發現手機內的電池漲起，也許是因為此原因，而導致螢幕爆裂並向外拱起。而台灣亦有《蘋果日報》的讀者向他們表示，其 iPhone 8 Plus 在充電時亦出現電池漲起，致螢幕爆裂並向外拱起的情況。而據韓國財經傳媒《Hankyung》介紹所示，iPhone 8 系列的電池生產商為 Samsung 旗下的 SDI，與之前爆炸事故頻生的 Samsung Note 7 採用同廠電池，未知今回是個別事件，還是電池真的發生了問題？不過，iPhone 8 Plus 在問題頻生的情況下，還沒入手的蘋果迷會為之卻步嗎？"},{"pid":"36e867e85f8b49c63af5ae24b7f343c9a29474bb","tid":417769,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/114401_22b277279d5fdb3a58a651dee6ba197a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F114401_22b277279d5fdb3a58a651dee6ba197a.jpg&h=7b0f7280&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/114402_4f97cf8dfc9233c9b275638e7072f34f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F114402_4f97cf8dfc9233c9b275638e7072f34f.jpg&h=7cd57361&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b49326944127d841eb576d5e41f9fdcc68632fb6","tid":417769,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"日本人有誠信，呢單嘢係真嘅"},{"pid":"65757e9840ced1a89d040163d5d65116462aa543","tid":417769,"uid":66997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人有誠信，呢單嘢係真嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩...宇宙大自慧嚟"},{"pid":"f109f5b5a293b1ee225bc3766100c9c8ad3595a3","tid":417769,"uid":93190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0